br.usp.ime.oneintegration
Class OneIntegration

java.lang.Object
  br.usp.ime.oneintegration.OneIntegration

public class OneIntegration
extends java.lang.Object

Class that performs the integration with the ONE simulator's output reports. For a given report, this class can generate the ONE router classes for the foremost, shortest, fastest and several middle optimal journeys. The report files are taken directly from the ONE directory and it is assumed this directory is in the same folder as the EvolvingGraphs directory.

Author:
Cesar Gamboa Machado, Paulo Henrique Floriano
